# `gale hook` is restricted to direnv. Per 537d53e (RO-J:
# hook help matches actual behaviour), cobra's OnlyValidArgs
# rejects unknown shells with "invalid argument" before
# the runtime ErrUnsupportedShell path is reached.

! exec gale hook bash
stderr 'invalid argument "bash" for "gale hook"'

! exec gale hook zsh
stderr 'invalid argument "zsh" for "gale hook"'
